These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, balloon-flower, azalea, lily
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, soul, techno, blues
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, snowmobile, subway, van
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person who growslily is on the left of the fan of techno##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of techno##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the fan of soul is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Flower    | balloon-flower  | lily | azalea    | amaryllis       |
| Music-Genre         | soul | blues    | techno      | hip-hop |
| Transport   | bike   | subway | snowmobile | van        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, broccoli, corn, pear
City: san-francisco, liverpool, nizza, hamburg
4 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon, domino, whist
1. the person playing whist is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person eating pear is on the right of the person playing domino##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person eating corn##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing whist##1
5. the person playing monopoly is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
6. the person playing whist is the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | corn   | broccoli | asparagus     | pear      |
| City         | liverpool | nizza | hamburg | san-francisco |
| Game   | backgammon    | whist   | domino     | monopoly      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, volleyball, water-polo, cycling
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, turtle, bird, mouse
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, indonesian, russian
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the canadian is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is the owner of the bird##1
5. the russian is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
6. the russian is on the right of the indonesian##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Sport         | lacrosse | volleyball | water-polo | cycling |
| Pet   | mouse       | turtle    | rabbit | bird     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | indonesian    | russian | canadian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, purple, aquamarine, lilac
City: prague, boston, hamburg, venice
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, taxi, train
1. the person who likes aquamarine is the person driving the train##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the person who likes purple is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
6. the person traveling to prague is the person who likes aquamarine##1
7. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
8. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Color         | azure | lilac | aquamarine | purple |
| City       | boston     | venice      | prague     | hamburg      |
| Transport   | motorbike | jet-ski         | train      | taxi        |

