.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
House: palace, cottage, craftsman, colonial
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, horror, thriller, western
4 different pets are kept: pony, horse, mouse, guinea-pig
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
2. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the owner of the pony is the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the palace house is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
6. the palace house is the person watching horror movies##1
7. the colonial house is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| House         | craftsman   | colonial | cottage  | palace      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | epic        | western  | horror       |
| Pet         | pony | mouse    | horse | guinea-pig |

