.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic, writer
There 4 different types of food: cherry, pomegranate, asparagus, orange
4 different pets are kept: dog, fish, chinchilla, rabbit
1. the accountant is the owner of the fish##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person eating cherry is on the right of the writer##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
5. the designer is on the far left##1
6. the person eating asparagus is the mechanic##1
7. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
8. the writer is the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | designer | mechanic | writer | accountant |
| Food   | orange   | asparagus  | pomegranate | cherry   |
| Pet   | rabbit   | dog     | chinchilla | fish       |

