.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, rose, amaryllis, sunflower
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, airplane, roller, train
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, spy, thriller
1. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
8. the person driving the airplane is the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Flower          | begonia  | sunflower | amaryllis   | rose     |
| Transport         | train | airplane   | tram  | roller |
| Movie-Genre   | spy         | disaster  | mystery | thriller  |

