.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, collecting, filmmaking, gardening
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, crime, drama, mystery
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, december, august, october
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby      | gardening | filmmaking     | skydiving | collecting |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | animation | drama       | crime    |
| Birthday   | december   | october | june    | august |

