.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, firefighter, security-guard, musician
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, jazz, punk
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, fuchsia, yellow, lavender
1. the fan of d&b is on the right of the musician##1
2. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
4. the person who likes yellow is the firefighter##1
5. the firefighter is on the right of the fan of punk##1
6. the fan of punk is on the right of the security-guard##1
7. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job          | security-guard        | musician   | firefighter  | dressmaker   |
| Music-Genre   | blues         | punk     | d&b    | jazz       |
| Color         | fuchsia | lilac | yellow | lavender |

