.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, iced-tea, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, singing, photography, card-games
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker, bridge, chess
1. the person drinking mirinda is the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person playing chess##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person playing chess##1
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | fanta    | iced-tea | mirinda | 7up        |
| Hobby       | card-games | puzzles  | singing | photography     |
| Game        | poker    | bridge   | chess  | mah-jongg |

