.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, guinea-pig, ferret, fish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, folk, dubstep, ambient
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, car, scooter, tram
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
2. the fan of classical is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
4. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
7. the fan of classical is the person driving the scooter##1
8. the fan of dubstep is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Pet         | hedgehog  | fish | guinea-pig  | ferret |
| Music-Genre       | dubstep | folk        | ambient | classical       |
| Transport   | airplane   | car          | tram          | scooter       |

