.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, cooking, dancing, traveling
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, dubstep, rock, soul
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, fisherman, journalist, dancer
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
2. the fan of soul is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the dancer is on the left of the firefighter##1
4. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is the journalist##1
7. the dancer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling   | dancing   | card-games | cooking |
| Music-Genre   | rock | electronic | dubstep   | soul |
| Job   | dancer     | firefighter  | journalist  | fisherman  |

