.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, reading, traveling
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, aristoff, game, blend
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, apricot, aquamarine, black
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is the blend-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes black##1
5. the person who likes red is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
7. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling | chess    | baking        | reading |
| Cigar   | aristoff     | game     | blend        | cain   |
| Color         | apricot   | red | aquamarine | black  |

