.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, drama, mystery, superhero
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, sprite, fanta
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, bolivar, montecristo, dunhill
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama   | superhero  | comedy    | mystery    |
| Beverage   | fanta | sprite  | juice  | hot-chocolate |
| Cigar     | dunhill  | bolivar | montecristo | cain        |

