.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, indonesian, dutch, chinese
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, yellow, black, green
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, handball, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is climbing is the dutch##1
2. the dutch is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
3. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes green##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person who likes green is the chinese##1
6. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the nigerian is the person who likes lilac##1
8. the person who likes black is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Nationality      | nigerian        | chinese    | indonesian | dutch      |
| Color   | lilac        | green   | yellow  | black  |
| Sport         | weightlifting | handball | soccer   | climbing |

