.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-19::.
4 different games are played: palaced-games, whist, monopoly, backgammon
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, chef, lawyer, nurse
House: cottage, palace, modern, wooden
1. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
2. the cottage house is on the right of the nurse##1
3. the lawyer is on the right of the nurse##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the chef##1
5. the palace house is on the far left##1
6. the person playing whist is on the right of the accountant##1
7. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |    3    |      4      |
| Game       | palaced-games | whist | backgammon | monopoly |
| Job         | accountant | chef  | nurse   | lawyer      |
| House   | palace        | modern  | wooden   | cottage         |

