.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, engineer, scientist, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, salsa, punk, reggae
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, frog, pony, lizard
1. the engineer is on the left of the fan of country##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the scientist##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
4. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
5. the fan of country is the owner of the pony##1
6. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
7. the security-guard is on the far right##1
8. the fan of reggae is on the left of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | engineer  | scientist  | dressmaker | security-guard |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | country | salsa   | punk      |
| Pet         | rabbit | pony    | frog   | lizard         |

 